Comment: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:32.75,sign,,0,0,0,,Healing Waters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my job as class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry! I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.30,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to wait until I get back to the classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortcut time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wipe off my indoor shoes after!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Are those—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-These are... bread crusts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You still eat as much as ever, Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is me holding back, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wonder how you eat so little, Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is more efficient than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to eat some of my side dishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter with the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you eating here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How bothersome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said "desu wa"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, a real rich girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to "hold back."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, now, what is the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we haven't introduced ourselves yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing Class 3 the favor of being their class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Doing them the favor"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Odagiri Futaba from the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet'cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I am Nishikawa Youko from Class 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're famous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Famous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, telling a student not to touch me\Nwith their filthy hands was not proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am not secretively eating alone\Nbecause nobody will eat with me after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, we weren't asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you are direct!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not have similar interests, and I do not\Nknow what to talk about in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking just fine right now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nice, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty fun to eat outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the first bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, bread crusts are yummy when you\Ndeep fry them and sprinkle sugar on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fry them and use sugar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of recipe is—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.05,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hurry, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Our teacher is strict about being on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We have English next, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What odd girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...that may have been my first lunch\Nwith others since I came to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is their class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I sorta got sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I so hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishikawa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it to the flash sale on time again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, bread crusts are yummy when you\Ndeep fry them and sprinkle sugar on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, do I have any sugar left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting a little full of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever do you mean, Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you badmouthed Kondo to the teacher yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was deliver the printouts to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For Kondo, the one on duty, since she\Ndidn't do her job for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, I want to settle things with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be too hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't take orders from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I was talking to Hayama, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they'll think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not as if I was expecting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I can eat lunch alone, like usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, that sucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Futaba...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted take a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't want to keep Yoko waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Five whole minutes late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, a nuisance picked a fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She cried at the end for some reason, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Best not to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a perv?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a stalker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a former family servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I sincerely apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What— Yamaji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was laboring under a misapprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was just a whim yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was here yesterday, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would accept a whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's a miracle for Miss Yoko to make school friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, a ruined shadow of the\Nrich young lady you once were,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,yet unable to let go of your upper-class\Nattitude after the company's bankruptcy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,due to your pampered upbringing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to make friends with normal commoners\Nat school must surely be a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamaji's exaggerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Miss Yoko forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As her school friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Er, listen, my—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it nice to be outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much fun to eat surrounded by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I {\i1}knew{\i0} you couldn't really make friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.10,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How horribly noisy they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd at least like to quietly enjoy a book during break time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These loud voices aren't ladylike at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I be social with such people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yoko! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Her smile is so bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I forgot my math textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My class doesn't have math today so I didn't bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In the old days, I would have had a servant fetch it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's not {\i1}that{\i0} big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,About the textbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries, it's my bad for forgetting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And she hardly pays attention\Nin class anyway, book or no book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, Hayama, you say the\Nrudest things with no hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Didn't I speak the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what white bread is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but why are you eating a whole loaf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Buying more than one thing is too much work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you having bread crusts again, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how many you can get for such little money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so moved the first time I saw these!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you need more nutrients?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're perfectly nutritious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to call the police if you keep trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm authorized to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I refill the school vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a side job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see!}Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stalkers are not fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That is unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about my quietly watching her unseen\Nfrom the shadows makes you think I'm a stalker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just concerned for Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No sooner had I taken over my late grandfather's\Nposition as servant than I was suddenly let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so worried about how the young miss\Nwill get along among the common folk,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She has such an explosive temper,\Nand when she doesn't get her way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it triggers a chemical reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, take these!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're clearance goods from my job,\Nbut they're not {\i1}quite{\i0} expired yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamaji, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, my next job is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If he pities you that much, he should give you cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he's barely making ends meet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I can't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he think {\i1}these{\i0} will make me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Drat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've been mortified, thanks to Yamaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally made friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to make sure not to turn them off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, here is today's expired food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does he have to do this during lunchtime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep a cool head, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't jump for joy and make them think you have no decorum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful! It's cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, cheese is healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you two, what are your favorite foods?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,White rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread kinda feels like a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I like rice better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not pack your own lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No time in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your fave, Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it's mille-feuille!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I like salted fish paste, is there a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that stuff is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Goes nicely with rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's yours, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to give an answer they won't think is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Something commoners would accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I like pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pudding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But that would be {\i1}gross{\i0} with rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With rice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are normal people's favorite foods\Nthings that pair well with rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to answer right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How about pink codfish flakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At least that's the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you used to be rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, they might start to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They were so happy about\Nthe fried bread crusts, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...I made rice balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she and bread crusts were exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can cook if I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind sharing, if you'd like some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't mean balls of {\i1}just{\i0} rice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is just rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you liked rice, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice balls are surprisingly complex, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of different possible fillings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,These have no fillings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,None?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to use salted fish paste,\Nsince Hayama likes it, but it was expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For my sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But in rice balls...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting the salt level in the rice right is tricky, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to add the salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did I fail again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they'd be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Listen, please don't force yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice is tasty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Futaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Yoko, you gotta eat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have one of my Vienna sausages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having thirds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do anything for me in return, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Since we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy, Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They were free tickets anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a family member who wins this stuff a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's here{ we are}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A bathhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing better than a bath for we Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since\NI could stretch my legs out in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...to heat enough water for a bath this big...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How much must the utility bills be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I lost it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To think they were even willing to bathe with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried, but I think Miss Yoko will survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't waste Hayama's kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop worrying and have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Another hour... no, at least half a daaay...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get dizzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna boil into Yoko soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Sonobe Shino.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Nishikawa family's former maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative,\Nthe poor girl on a daily bread-crust diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Their "to each her own color" life is so entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.53,0:23:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so my tumultuous school life began.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This new dog eat dog world is full of trials,\Nsuch as understanding how to spend break time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.85,0:23:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But from now on, I won't lunch alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we eat indoors when it rains?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.15,0:23:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
